'''赫柏·卡爾·延奇'''（{{lang-en|Heber Carl Jentzsch}}；{{bd|1935年|11月30日||}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/news/10-000-scientologists-got-this-e-mail-today-about-disconnection-their-church-president-and-a-mysterious-death-6723502|title=10,000 Scientologists Got This E-Mail Today About "Disconnection," their Church President, and a Mysterious Death|last=Ortega|first=Tony|date=2012-07-09|website=Village Voice|access-date=2016-05-15|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116080545/http://www.villagevoice.com/news/10-000-scientologists-got-this-e-mail-today-about-disconnection-their-church-president-and-a-mysterious-death-6723502|dead-url=no}}</ref>），從1982年起就是國際山達基教會的總裁。他在2004年以後就沒有公開的活動<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2170405/Scientology-Son-Church-president-Heber-Jentzsch-troubled-life.html?ITO=1490 The troubled life of Scientology president's son] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2170405/Scientology-Son-Church-president-Heber-Jentzsch-troubled-life.html?ITO=1490 |date=20210127112206 }}, ''Daily Mail'', 8 July 2012.</ref>。

==生平==
1935年，赫柏·延奇出生於鹽湖城<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.villagevoice.com/runninscared/2012/07/scientology_heber_jentzsch_karen_de_la_carriere_email.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-07-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711223401/http://blogs.villagevoice.com/runninscared/2012/07/scientology_heber_jentzsch_karen_de_la_carriere_email.php |archivedate=2012-07-11 }} ''Village Voice'', 10 July 2012.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=ybE9AQAAIAAJ&q=Heber+Jentzsch+1935&dq=Heber+Jentzsch+1935&hl=en&sa=X&ei=uKqMVfGKCdWEyQTCnJOYAw&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2016-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022120132/https://books.google.ca/books?id=ybE9AQAAIAAJ&q=Heber+Jentzsch+1935&dq=Heber+Jentzsch+1935&hl=en&sa=X&ei=uKqMVfGKCdWEyQTCnJOYAw&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAg |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成長於一個[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]家庭<ref>{{cite episode | title = Inside the Church of Scientology | series = Larry King Live | serieslink = Larry King Live | airdate = 1993-12-20}}</ref>。

他是卡爾（Carl）<ref name="slctrib921209"/>與第三個妻子寶蓮（Pauline）的兒子；而赫柏·延奇有42個兄弟<ref>"Scientologists march on courthouse", UPI 20.5.1985</ref>。

赫柏·延奇在猶他州奧格登的[[韦伯州立大学|韦伯学院]]與[[猶他大學|猶他大學]]接受教育，畢業於1959年，取得一張傳播學的學歷<ref name="slctrib921209">"Utah-Born Scientology President Says the Religion Saved His Life", ''The Salt Lake Tribune'', 9.12.1992</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.alumni.utah.edu/u-news/april04/postit.htm |title=University of Utah Alumni Association, April 2004 |access-date=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021173318/https://www.alumni.utah.edu/u-news/april04/postit.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也學習東方宗教<ref name="naisbitt">Jentzsch biography in John Naisbitt, ''High Tech High Touch: Technology and Our Accelerated Search for Meaning'', p. 253. Nicholas Brealey Publishing, 2004.</ref>。

在1967年加入[[山達基教會|山達基教會]]之前，赫柏·延奇是《{{le|洛杉磯自由新聞|Los Angeles Free Press}}》的一名記者，與一名演員，曾在電影《{{le|長征萬寶山|Paint Your Wagon (film)}}》中參與演出<ref>{{cite journal | journal=LA Weekly| first=Ron|last=Curran|date=April 4, 1986 |volume=9 |issue=19|title=Scientology: The other side of the looking glass}}</ref><ref>{{cite episode |title=Scientology - The Road to Total Freedom?  |series=Panorama |serieslink=Panorama_(TV_series) |network=[[BBC|BBC]] |station=BBC1 |airdate=27 April 1987 }}</ref>。

1988年12月，山達基教會總裁赫柏·延奇，在西班牙被捕，經調查後發現，他和山達基教會詐騙西班牙公民，和在那可拿中心使用不合格的工作人員。<ref>Stephen Koff ''[http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/51427830.html?dids=51427830:51427830&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Nov+22%2C+1988&author=STEPHEN+KOFF&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=1.A&desc=Top+Scientologist+arrested+in+Spain "Top Scientologist Arrested in Spain"] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/51427830.html?dids=51427830:51427830&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Nov+22%2C+1988&author=STEPHEN+KOFF&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=1.A&desc=Top+Scientologist+arrested+in+Spain |date=20071127164621 }}'' [[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]] November 22, 1988 pg. 1A</ref>  西班牙公民開始频繁的拨打電話至法院，抱怨遭到那可拿蒙蔽。法官在案件的新聞發布會上說，山達基唯一的上帝的是金錢。他並說，那可拿騙客戶和吸引他們到山達基。<ref>Steven Koff ''[http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/51435991.html?dids=51435991:51435991&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Dec+10%2C+1988&author=STEPHEN+KOFF&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=21.A&&pf=1 "Scientology leader still jailed in Spain; church charges 'persecution'"] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/51435991.html?dids=51435991:51435991&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Dec+10%2C+1988&author=STEPHEN+KOFF&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=21.A&&pf=1 |date=20071127163836 }}'' [[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]] December 10, 1988</ref> 1989年，75個山達基信徒在意大利被逮捕，調查表明，“吸毒者父母付出沉重的月費，但沒有得到任何回報。”<ref>Ruth Gruber ''[http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/50427369.html?dids=50427369:50427369&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Mar+29%2C+1989&author=RUTH+E.+GRUBER&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=11.A&desc=75+Scientologists+go+on+trial+today+%2F%2F+%60It+should+be+a+lively+court+session%27&pf=1 "75 Scientologists go on trial today // 'It should be a lively court session'"] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/50427369.html?dids=50427369:50427369&FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Mar+29%2C+1989&author=RUTH+E.+GRUBER&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&edition=&startpage=11.A&desc=75+Scientologists+go+on+trial+today+%2F%2F+%60It+should+be+a+lively+court+session%27&pf=1 |date=20071127163833 }}'' [[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]] Mar 29, 1989 pg. 11.A</ref>

2012年7月2日，亞歷山大·延奇（Alexander Jentzsch）（赫柏·延奇與卡倫·德拉·卡里埃（Karen de la Carriere）的兒子）在一場事故中死亡<ref>{{cite web |author=Beth Stebner |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2170405/Scientology-Son-Church-president-Heber-Jentzsch-troubled-life.html |title=Scientology: Son of Church president Heber Jentzsch had troubled life | Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2012-07-08 |accessdate=2013-01-11 |archive-date=2017-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517173424/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2170405/Scientology-Son-Church-president-Heber-Jentzsch-troubled-life.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

